### 3. CI/CD Pipeline

[ci-cd.yml](file:///c:/Users/91901/OneDrive/Desktop/practice2/.github/workflows/ci-cd.yml) — 3-job pipeline:

```
Job 1: lint-and-test (4 services in parallel matrix)
    ↓
Job 2: build-and-push (5 services, Docker build + Trivy scan + DockerHub push)
    ↓
Job 3: update-helm-values (updates image tags → triggers ArgoCD sync)
```

